dc_description_s: These data layers represent public lands for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, NWashburn_PublicLands_2018.gdbN. The features included in this geodatabase are NWashburn_County_Forest_2018N, NWashburn_DNR_Lands_2018N, and NWashburn_Federal_Lands_2018N.[County Forest: The County Lands layer for Washburn County is intended to represent County Lands referenced in the taxroll as described in legal descriptions and surveys. The polygons were extracted from the Tax Parcel polygons utilizing ownership information from the Tax Roll.Federal Lands: The Federal Lands layer for Washburn County is intended to represent Federal Lands referenced in the taxroll as described in legal descriptions and surveys. The polygons were extracted from the Tax Parcel polygons utilizing ownership information from the Tax Roll.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
